   <h1> About us </h1>

   <p> AllerGenius is a nonprofit website created by <a href="https://www.kodewithklossy.com/">Kode with Klossy</a> scholars Maya Griffith and Lauren Chan. Both Maya and Lauren have severe food allergies, and often feel excluded or unsafe when eating out, because their allergens are all around them. They created this because they wanted to help people like them.
