<h2> Maya Griffith </h2>
<p>Maya Griffith is a junior in Old Tappan Regional High School and lives in Harrington Park, New Jersey. She loves dancing, specifically ballet, field hockey, lacrosse, and makeup. Maya is allergic to many things including nuts, peanuts, sesame, and several others, and has had allergies to many other foods including dairy, shellfish, and eggs in the past.  But, even being allergic to all of these things, she does not let it hold her back. Creating his website is extremely important to her because she knows what it is like to not ever feel safe when eating.<p>
