<h2> Lauren Chan </h2>

<p>Lauren Chan is a sophomore in West Windsor-Plainsboro High School North, and currently lives in Princeton, New Jersey. She loves competitively swimming, reading, and being outside. She created this website in hopes of creating a safer environment for those with food allergies, since she used to be allergic to coconuts, eggs, and nuts. She currently still has a severe allergy to dairy, which has created some problems in everyday life. However, she uses her struggle to fuel her passion for this website.
</p>



